snippet.title: MOGA is back: Monster Galaxy P2E Official Trailer!
snippet.description:
Monster Galaxy is back with an exciting new chapter! The great Zodiac has become mysteriously misaligned and now it's up to you to set things right. Visit familiar lands and venture to unexplored corners of the world! Recover the twelve long-lost Zodiac relics and restore balance to the Galaxy. Your story starts here…
 
Battle, Tame, Earn. Embark on an adventure to be the greatest Tamer in the galaxy!
 
#MonsterGalaxy #MOGA 
 
Download for FREE!
App Store: https://rebrand.ly/MonsterGalaxyAppStore
Google Play: https://rebrand.ly/MonsterGalaxyGooglePlay
 
Follow us for all the latest updates:
Official Website: www.playmonstergalaxy.com

Discord: https://discord.gg/monstergalaxy
